# Gameplay loop

2-4 PvP free-for all fast paced capture-the-zone style

\-Very raw movement and shooting, quake style, bunnyhopping, walljumping and vaulting  
\- no bullshit recoil or spread, literally click and hit, hitscan weapons(see more in weapons category)

1. Game start ( 10 minutes)  
2. Players spawn in one way zone, grace period to capture other zones ( 2 minutes grace, can respawn in that period)  
3. Players enter buffer zones, pvp enabled there, can pickup weapons  
4. Players rush to a grey/white zone (there are multiple zones), available for capturing, once captured lights up as player colours, and sets it as spawn point, can capture as many zones as possible (around 15 seconds to capture, starting capture sends a lightwave in radius to alert other players), players can only heal incrementally in zones every 5 seconds  
5. Other players can try to contest it  
6. For each second player has zone captured it adds to a score (see scoring system)  
7. If player dies, they can respawn at the captured zone grace period is over, hoever its perma death if player doesnt have any captured zones, but losing zones doesnt kill player, so it gives them a second chance at retaking a zone  
8. Once the zone is in retake/capture mode, environment in such zone becomes animated, moving randomly creating more dynamic to it.  
9. Last man standing doesnt mean win, scoring system is preferred

## Scoring system

(score cant be lower than 0\)  
Player kill \+ 10 score  
Stylish player kill (airborne, wallbang) \+ 40 score  
Grey zone capture \+ 100 score  
Player zone capture \+ 200 score  
Player zone lost \- 150 score  
Grey Mid zone capture \+ 150 score

## Weapons 

All weapons are hitscan, meaning they dont have delay after shot  
All weapons can wallbang with 50% damage reduction  
Automatic weapons can ricochet from surfaces with angle less than 30 degrees

Type of weapons:  
\-Pistol: can 1 tap everywhere except limbs  
\-Auto-rifle: high distance damage reduction, good at close range  
\-Semi-auto: long reload, explosive rounds on impact  
\-Sniper-rifle: long delay between shots, 100% wallbang penetration  
All weapons can be carried at once, however ammunition is shared
